quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  2,272,"A fawaaki peewal mum en kono ko Alla feewnata mbo O faala, kala ko tottirЙ—on e moЖҙЖҙere ko ko*e mon woodani on nafkatah si wonah ngam Alla kala ko tottirЙ—on e moЖҙЖҙere tottite Й—um e mbaadi timmundi onon de on tooГұetaake"
  2,273,"Woodanii waasЙ“e suraaЙ“e gaa e laawol Alla Й“e mbaawah yaade e leydi hee, majjuЙ“e na cikka koЙ“e alЙ—uЙ“e sabu Й—uurnaade aduna ana anndiraЙ“e maandeeji mum en Й“e Гұaagataaka yimЙ“e e mbaadi cattundi kala ko tottirЙ—on Alla na anndi Й—um"
  2,274,"TootirooЙ“e jawdi mum en jemma e Гұalawma e mbaadi mbirniindi e mbaadi Й“anngundi, Й“een de woodaniiЙ“e njbdi mum en ummaade ka joomi mum en kulol woodanaani Й“e Й“e ngonah sunatooЙ“e"
  2,275,"Й“een ГұaamooЙ“e riba Й“e ummataako si wonah no mbo seytaani memi Й—uum noon ko sabu wiide Й“e pellet njeegu wa*i kono riba, Alla noon daknii njeeygu O harmini riba, kala mbo waaju ummmarii mbo ka Alla o acci woodanii mbo o Й“enni ko fiyaaku makko e Alla fawii, kala duttiiЙ—o noon ko Й“een ngoni joman en yiite saasooЙ“e e henge haa pooma"
  2,276,Alla na momto riba na Й“amta sadakuuji Alla yiЙ—ah kala keeЙ—o keefeeru e bakkadinoowo sanne
  2,277,Й“een goonЙ—inЙ“e ngolli ko moЖҙЖҙi o darni juulde o tottiri askal woodaniiЙ“e jobdi mum en ummaade ko joomi mum en kulol alanaaЙ“e Й“e ngonah sunatooЙ“e
  2,278,Eehey mon goonЙ—inЙ“e kulee Alla accon ko heddii ko e riba si on ngonii goonЙ—uЙ“e
  2,279,Si on mbaЙ—aani Й—uum kolliree hare ummorde e Alla e nelaaЙ—o MakkoJJJЙ“J
  2,280,"Si tawii o wonii e satteende yo o muГұane haa e yaajeende,nde cakkorton Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude e mon si on ngonii annduЙ“e"
  2,281,Kulee Гұalngu ngu ndutteteЙ—on ka Alla refti yoЙ“ee kala fittaandu ko ndu faggitii ko kamЙ“e Й“e tooГұetaake
  2,282,"Eehey mon goonЙ—inЙ“e si on Гұamlandiri nyamaande faade happu dottaaЙ—o mbinndee nde, yo nuunЙ—uЙ—o winndu hakkunde mon, woto binndoowo sala winndude yo o winndu no Alla anndiniri mbo, yo o winndu yo mbo hakke woni dow mum winndu yo o hul joomiiko woto o ustu heen hay huunde, si wonii mbo hakke woni e dow mum ko Й—aayЙ—o wolla lohЙ—o wollo o waawah fidde, yo keedo makko fidir nuunЙ—al, ceednee seede en Й—iЙ—o e worЙ“e mon, si worЙ“e Й—iЙ—o ngalah ko gorko e rewЙ“e Й—iЙ—o Й“e mbelete Й—on e seedeeli ngam si gooto e maЙ“Й“e yrdditi goЙ—Й—o o siftirina mbo, woto seedeeli cala siЙ“e noddaama, wote kaaste winndude ko famЙ—i maa ko heewi faade e happu mum, ko Й—uum Й“uri nuunЙ—ude ka Alla Й“uri fooccaade wonande seede Й“uri kadi Й“adaade waasde mon sikkitaade, si wonah kommersaagu ngonaangu ngu yiilaton hakkunde mon, ndeen noon bakkaat alah e mon nde mbaasaton Й—um winndude, ceetnee si on yeeyandiri woto binndoowo e seede lore, si on waЙ—ii Й—uum pellet Й—uum ko faasikaagal e mon, kulee Alla O anndina on Alla ko kattanЙ—o kala huunde"